[i]Imprint[/i] – When this artifact enters, you may exile an instant, sorcery, or Aura spell from your hand.
Whenever equipped creature deals combat damage to a player, you may copy a spell exiled with this artifact with mana value less than or equal to the damage dealt. You may cast the copy without paying its mana cost. [i](Auras become tokens.)[/i]
